                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The sacristans stare at a creature they can see within 30 feet. The creature must immediately attempt a @Check[will|dc:33] save against staggering servitude. In addition, if the creature was already stunned, on a failed save its revulsion toward the sacristans' presence causes it to be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} for 1 minute. After attempting this save, the creature is then temporarily immune to staggering servitude until the start of the scourge's next turn.</p>"
                },
