                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The scourge lashes with barbed chains against enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:33|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions. A creature that critically fails is also knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone].</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d8[piercing],1d6[spirit],1d4[bleed]]{1d8 piercing plus 1d6 spirit and 1d4 persistent bleed}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(3d8+6)[piercing],1d6[spirit],1d6[bleed]]{3d8+6 piercing plus 1d6 spirit and 1d6 persistent bleed}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(4d8+9)[piercing],1d6[spirit],1d8[bleed]]{4d8+9 piercing plus 1d6 spirit and 1d8 persistent bleed}</p>"
